data.description: Look no further. You just found an adorable white picket fence, 3-bedroom 1-bath home. New laminate floors, paint. Enjoy your morning coffee or BBQ under the covered patio with retractable awning. Large backyard with a shed for extra storage. Roomy 2-Garage with work bench and additional storage Extra parking in driveway. and don't forget about your white picket fence front yard. Close to shopping and dining.
